uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連仔有無興趣幫區議會寫個全民監察apps"},{"pid":"6ccec0fa172696555e5eea97b67b3b17c3f69c1b","tid":1755286,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"另一個大家可以參考的條目：<br />\n劉肇軒<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E8%82%87%E8%BB%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E8%2582%2587%25E8%25BB%2592&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmR4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=9a4a667f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E8%82%87%E8%BB%92</a>"},{"pid":"f6718582145712400ae336106468b8d9a3237a97","tid":1755286,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"而家好多區議員都已經有條目。<br />\n希望大家可以click入去睇下，搵下有冇啲咩曾經上過新聞嘅事跡已寫入去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2019%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmR4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=3aac7802\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔知可唔可以寫、唔識寫都可以喺度發問。"}]}